data.description: ''Charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in the heart of Surprise, AZ! This beautifully maintained property  offers an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, spacious kitchen with newer Saltillo flooring, and a large backyard. Home has NEW AC/unit, and water softener. Enjoy the Arizona sunsets from your private patio or explore the nearby parks and amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!''
